net.cloud.gfx.elements

Class PasswordField

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.cloud.gfx.elements.AbstractElement
      • net.cloud.gfx.elements.TextField
        • net.cloud.gfx.elements.PasswordField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Element, Focusable

    public class PasswordField
extends TextField
    A text field where rather than showing the actual text in the field, asterisks are used instead. The hint text is still shown. Everything else works just like with a text field, you can still change settings and obtain the true text.
